Package projects.pqueue.trees

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    A BinarySearchTree is a Tree with a maximum of 2 children nodes per nodes which allows for adding and removing nodes in a sorted manner.
    Tree<T>
    A standard interface for a tree-like data structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinkedBinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    LinkedBinarySearchTree is an implementation of a BinarySearchTree using links.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyTreeException
    A Exception thrown by tree-based data structures when the tree is empty.
